headline: Will Altria's Stock Continue to Be a Dividend Darling?
summary: Altria continues to see large cigarette volume declines.  It is offsetting declines with big price increases, but this could reach a tipping point in the future.  Altria Group (NYSE: MO) has long been a dividend darling that attracts investors looking for a high yield.
